Class ServerEntityManager

java.lang.Object
de.oth.blocklib.entities.EntityManager
de.oth.blocklib.server.ServerEntityManager
public class ServerEntityManager
extends EntityManager
The EntityManager for the server to handle the entities and message the clients about it
The WorldGenerator must be build before the ServerEntityManager is build
Author:
Florian Mayer
